{"type": "article", "id": 13765, "title": "Muji 厨房用品", "description": "", "date": "2015-08-20T07:45:24Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 17, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606140507VyuBrxcH7U4Q1P8d.png", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t设计师 Naoto Fukasawa 为 Muji 推出了一套厨房用品，包括一个茶壶和一个烤面包机。遵循其一贯的极简设计路线，两件产品都采用原白色，外观上采用圆形的设计，开关等设计在产品的同一面，并进行极简化的处理，看上去憨态可掬。两件产品刚刚登陆美国市场，并将于 11 月份登陆英国市场，明年扩展到全欧洲。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141443At2QzZVK8HTkygsq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.715\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141444JRkphTyOCiZMGKev.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.715\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141444ld4yLGcMTQAikSgr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.715\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141444s5PSvcMhLjCgnAwY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.715\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141445inE7rJO83NKxj49D.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.715\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141445VtjLmC0yJa6IE5nG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.715\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141445DMXWrp6f4CSiIGKL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.715\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141446NgtluwKVC5U6dMvI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.715\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141446youlR0jxKvkE1z2I.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6675\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}